title: Indonesia fights toxic waste in a vital river
text:
Indonesia fights toxic waste in a vital river 3:20am EST - 01:45 
A massive seven-year cleaning operation is underway to clean up a trash-strewn Indonesian river which is known to be one of the world's most polluted rivers.
